{"tid":2016570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌、賴弘國 昔日情史各自精采","createTime":"2020-05-14T13:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T11:48:50.000Z","uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e022a1613cc4a7dd08237a4449463b941637ce6","tid":2016570,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"鍾欣潼(阿嬌)前年嫁給交往三個月的「醫界王陽明」賴弘國，結婚不到兩年就離婚。阿嬌當年與蔡卓妍(阿Sa)組成偶像女團「Twins」，一度風靡華人娛樂圈，阿嬌先後與陳冠希、余文樂以及麥浚龍傳出緋聞，她也在受訪時證實曾與陳冠希交往四、五年。阿嬌與余文樂在2002年拍攝電影「一碌蔗」時結緣相戀，一度還傳出余文樂、陳冠希曾在頒獎典禮慶功宴上為了她大打出手。阿嬌後來拍攝港片「破事兒」則與麥浚龍相戀，但隔年阿嬌與陳冠希的「豔照門」事件震驚各界，阿嬌更開記者會表示「最愛陳冠希」，隔沒多久之後也與麥浚龍分手。<br />\n<br />\n賴弘國外型高大帥氣，又是知名醫師，歷任女友也都是條件優秀的美女，他曾與節目「我愛黑澀會」的美眉Suan（陳瑋萱）交往過，又與有「華航林依晨」封號的美女空姐趙筱葳(Ivy)曾有過半年的短命婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>source：worldjournal.com</code>"},{"pid":"12273617a4d575e1a276ba421bbf1c0cf762d453","tid":2016570,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFQXH5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFQXH5J.jpg&h=47c43332&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03478ccfbcb84bcb8335fabef2c68432e1a4360b","tid":2016570,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eA4Q26d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeA4Q26d.jpg&h=f6485731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0456de65144ca39476f3ef078213220d6565579","tid":2016570,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"真係大眾雞嚟"},{"pid":"ee4ea37517b13b27c57041ae10a6bfae59205b76","tid":2016570,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/next-photos/NextMag/934/640pixfolder/E934-019N/578021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F93